      "contentBlocks": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "data": {
            "content": "# 认识 Do Re Mi 🎶\n\n在简谱中，我们用数字来表示音符。今天先学习最基础的三个音：\n\n| 数字 | 唱名 | 读音 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 1 | Do | 哆 |\n| 2 | Re | 来 |\n| 3 | Mi | 咪 |"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "audio",
          "data": {
            "notes": [60, 62, 64],
            "labels": ["1 (Do)", "2 (Re)", "3 (Mi)"],
            "instruction": "点击听一听每个音的声音"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "data": {
            "content": "## 在键盘上找到它们\n\n在钢琴键盘上：\n- **1 (Do)** 是「中央 C」，是学琴的起点\n- **2 (Re)** 在 Do 的右边\n- **3 (Mi)** 在 Re 的右边\n\n它们都是白键，依次排列。"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "piano",
          "data": {
            "startMidi": 60,
            "endMidi": 67,
            "showLabels": true,
            "labelType": "jianpu",
            "highlightNotes": [60, 62, 64],
            "instruction": "高亮的键就是 1、2、3，试着弹一弹"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "data": {
            "content": "## 跟我唱\n\n让我们一起唱出这三个音：\n\n🎵 **Do - Re - Mi**\n\n🎵 **1 - 2 - 3**\n\n反复练习几遍，记住它们的音高！"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "data": {
            "content": "## 小练习\n\n试着在钢琴上弹出以下旋律：\n\n**1 2 3 2 1**\n\n（Do Re Mi Re Do）"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "piano",
          "data": {
            "startMidi": 60,
            "endMidi": 67,
            "showLabels": true,
            "labelType": "jianpu",
            "targetSequence": [60, 62, 64, 62, 60],
            "instruction": "按顺序弹出 1 2 3 2 1"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "quiz",
